# vhs tape — records the bundled offline demo for README.md
# Regenerate: npm run build && vhs docs/demo.tape   (output: docs/demo.gif)
Output docs/demo.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 620
Set Padding 12
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Type "npx termfc demo --speed 300"
Enter
# entrance animation + full match at 300x (~2h07m of wall clock ≈ 26s) + FT screen
Sleep 33s
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
